description: Atlantic Sapphire ASA, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the production and sale of land-based salmon in Denmark and the United States. The company offers its product under Bluehouse Salmon, and Sapphire Salmon brand name. It serves retailers, restaurants, and other customers. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Vikebukt, Norway.
